articles.title: Europe's far-right split on Trump's Ukraine squeeze - Axios
articles.description: It has caught even some of his reliable allies on the continent off guard.
articles.content:
Europe's far-right leaders are divided over President Trump's approach to ending the Russia-Ukraine war.
Why it matters: Trump's embrace of Russian President Vladimir Putin and coinciding about-face… [+1548 chars]
